Syntax: COMMENT <#channel> ADD <comment>
        COMMENT <#channel> REM <id>
        COMMENT <#channel> LIST
 
This command is used for maintaining comments on <#channel>.
 
COMMENT ADD will add a comment to <#channel>.
COMMENT REM will remove a comment from the channel's comments list.
COMMENT LIST lists all comments on <#channel>.
 
